### AWS Tags

- You can add text key-value pairs called Tags to many AWS resources
- Commonly used in EC2
- Free naming, common tags are Name, Environment, Team …
- They’re used for
- Resource grouping
- Automation
- Cost allocation
- Better to have too many tags than too few!

