Stack D
Stack C
Stack E
Stack F

### Cross Stacks vs. Nested Stacks

App 1 Stack
- Cross Stacks
- Helpful when stacks have different lifecycles
- Use Outputs Export and Fn::ImportValue
- When you need to pass export values to
many stacks (VPC Id…)
