- Send EKS Control Plane audit and diagnostic logs
to CloudWatch Logs
- EKS Control Plane Log Types
- API Server (api)
- Audit (audit)
- Authenticator (authenticator)
- Controller Manager (controllerManager)
- Scheduler (scheduler)
- Ability to select the exact log types to send to
