### Amazon EKS – Nodes & Containers Logging

- You can capture node, pod, and containers logs
and send them to CloudWatch Logs
- Use CloudWatch Agent to send metrics to
CloudWatch
- Use the Fluent Bit, or Fluentd log drivers to
